  <section class="brand" id="brand">
    <h1 class="section-header">Brand Overview</h1>
    <p>Megabus is clean, sophisticated, young, and modern which we embody with this branding. This identity reflects how our clients view the brand so it is important to implement it as follows.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="logos" id="logos">
    <h1 class="section-header">Logos</h1>
    <img src="images/megabus-logo.svg" class="logo-size-horizontal">
    <img src="images/megabus-logo-bw.svg" class="logo-size-horizontal">
    <img src="images/megabus-logo-white.svg" class="off-black logo-size-horizontal">
    <div class="clearfix"></div>

    <h2>Usages &amp; Sizing</h2>
    <div class="left images">
        <img src="images/megabus-logo.svg" class="logo-size-medium">
    </div>
    <div class="left">
    <p>The logo and typography can be seperated and used without one another. Please only use these versions of the logo and do not make any alterations with design or spacing.</p>
        <p>The logotype can never be less than 1 inch in size. The mark can never be less than 1/2 an inch.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>

    <h2>On colors &amp; photography</h2>
    <div class="left images">
    <img src="images/megabus-photograph-white.jpg" class="images">
    <img src="images/megabus-photograph-no.jpg" class="images">
    </div>
    <div class="left">
    <p>The white verison looks best with dark backgrounds, the black with light, and the teal green with neutral. Please be mindful of keeping the logo prominant and visible. Use teal green on white or white on teal green when possible.</p>
     </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

    <h2>Rotation</h2>
    <div class="left images">
    <img src="images/megabus-logo-angled.svg" class="logo-size-horizontal">
    <img src="images/megabus-logo-vertical.svg" class="logo-size-vertical">
    <img src="images/megabus-logo-upsidedown.svg" class="logo-size-horizontal">
    </div>
    <div class="left">
    <p>Do not ever angle the logotype, mark, or wordmark. The wordmark can be rotated vertically with the typography facing upward with the m on the bottom and the s on the top.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>


  </section>

